Visually inspect results¶

fixed = reset_ants_img(load_allen()['template'])

for key, anat in Mice(load_preproc=True).T1w.items():
    moving = anat.get_data()
    moving = reorient_arr(moving)
    moving = reset_ants_img(moving)
    
    warped_file = next(x for x in os.listdir(Config().warped_dir) if key in x)
    warped = ants.image_read(pjoin(Config().warped_dir, warped_file))
    
    print(key)
    _ = plot_registration(
        fixed=fixed,
        moving=moving,
        warped=warped,
        sup=False,
        figsize=(4, 4.5),
    )
    print('\n\n\n')
